      "author": "XJain03",
      "description": "## What's New\n\n### Web Clipper Support\n- Auto-upload images when clipping articles with Obsidian Web Clipper\n- Detects new markdown files and processes all external image URLs\n- Replaces original URLs with PicX URLs automatically\n\n### Smart Image Detection\n- Handles all image formats: markdown, wikilink, nested links, HTML img tags\n- Skips GitHub badges, shields.io, charts (non-content images)\n- Decodes camo.githubusercontent.com URLs to bypass proxy timeouts\n\n### Bug Fixes\n- Fixed URL parsing that included markdown title text\n- Improved download reliability with fallback mechanisms\n\n### Commands\n- `Upload all external images in current note` - manually trigger upload for active note",
